    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m parting with my absolute favorite ride, and let me tell you, it\u2019s a beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, always reliable and honestly a total blast to drive. It\u2019s in wonderful shape\u2014mechanically sound and still turns heads whenever I\u2019m out and about. It has a little bit of that 'well-loved' character here and there, but that just means it's ready for real-world adventures without you worrying about the first scratch. It\u2019s a solid, honest car looking for a great new home!",
