    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously sorted performance icon. The high-revving power plant maintains rock-solid oil pressure and consistent compression across all cylinders, reflecting a life of stringent maintenance. I\u2019ve proactively addressed the common weak points, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and full subframe reinforcement to ensure maximum structural rigidity during high-load cornering. The suspension geometry has been dialed in with adjustable damping and upgraded poly-bushings for surgical turn-in and zero deflection. Power delivery is immediate through a precision-shimmed limited-slip differential and a crisp 6-speed gearbox featuring a lightweight flywheel for lightning-fast rev-matching. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a mechanically optimized platform where every fluid flush and torque spec has been documented. Ready for the track or the canyons, this machine is dialed in and free of any diagnostic codes or parasitic leaks.",
