      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute pride and joy. She\u2019s been a dream to drive and has never let me down on a weekend cruise. She\u2019s got a few tiny stories to tell on the paintwork if you look close enough, but honestly, she still turns heads at every stoplight. The engine purrs just like the day I got her, and the interior is still that cozy place you never want to leave. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate her as much as I have!",
